("clh4d6qjs000gtb0hr357gjvv","Tornado Demon","[{\"type\": \"statadjust\", \"power\": 20, \"elements\": [\"Wind\"], \"direction\": \"offence\", \"statTypes\": [\"Ninjutsu\", \"Genjutsu\"], \"calculation\": \"percentage\", \"description\": \"Adjust stats of target\", \"generalTypes\": [\"Willpower\", \"Intelligence\"], \"powerPerLevel\": 0.5}, {\"type\": \"healadjust\", \"power\": 10, \"elements\": [\"Wind\"], \"direction\": \"offence\", \"statTypes\": [\"Ninjutsu\", \"Genjutsu\"], \"calculation\": \"percentage\", \"description\": \"Adjust how much target can heal others\", \"generalTypes\": [\"Willpower\", \"Intelligence\"], \"powerPerLevel\": 0.5}]","The bloodline is a legendary lineage that imbues its bearers with an otherworldly mastery over the power of the wind. Those born with this bloodline possess an inherent connection to the elements, enabling them to manipulate the very air itself to devastating effect. The bloodline is a true testament to the power of the elements and the terrifying potential of those who can wield them.",0,"All","/bloodlines/tornado_demon.png","2023-05-01 04:52:39.784","2023-06-06 12:46:17.350","A",0),
